    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/org/morrison-vv40-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed per the MRL 2 assessment table — minimum requirements for those factors are satisfied by documentation alone. Hemolysis index validation error (8.7%) is within the 15% acceptance threshold. The computational model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in CPB service. UoA accepted for pre-market submission support.",
